(1) What is emmet?

Emmet is a plugin for text editors and IDEs that provides shortcuts for quickly writing and editing HTML and CSS code, it allows developers to work efficiently by using shorthand notation which is then expanded into full code. It also provides many other features that speed up the development process.

(2) What are the advantages of using emmet?

Emmet provides increased productivity, improved code readability, consistency and accuracy, dynamic tag and attribute generation, support for multiple text editors and IDEs, and a large community.

